309
00:30:28,767 --> 00:30:49,873
[SPEAKER_13]: And I think, Lily, am I correct in remembering that we were considering that there might actually be some, if the board is interested in having more members, if there's anybody who feels that they're overcommitted and needs to step down, there were a couple of additional new applicants that came in pretty recently that might be of interest as well.

310
00:30:51,775 --> 00:31:08,621
[SPEAKER_13]: So, but I thought we also kind of wanted to get the temperature of the board a little, because this is a board that does not need to come to consensus to make a decision to issue a permit, but rather looks for people to get stuff done and have volunteers to work on things and move stuff forward.

311
00:31:09,121 --> 00:31:13,963
[SPEAKER_13]: It's our feeling that more people are better than fewer for this board.

312
00:31:14,963 --> 00:31:19,345
