518
00:48:12,938 --> 00:48:25,265
[SPEAKER_08]: Just to be clear, that was about trying to prevent the use of toxic rodenticides to allow the natural predators to live.

519
00:48:25,646 --> 00:48:27,687
[SPEAKER_08]: And because they often die from eating

520
00:48:28,751 --> 00:48:33,816
[SPEAKER_08]: rodents, not just rats, that are eating rodenticides and they die an awful death.

