00:48:35,458 --> 00:48:40,263
[SPEAKER_08]: And there are other things that can be used besides rodenticides.

523
00:48:41,284 --> 00:48:47,310
[SPEAKER_08]: And so, you know, I had said to at the last meeting that I was working on a few things with the health department.

524
