[SPEAKER_08]: And I mentioned that to the mayor.

525
00:48:51,417 --> 00:49:05,733
[SPEAKER_08]: And one was to have another public meeting, education meeting with Yankee Pest Control that was done several, well, not just before COVID, where they gave an excellent presentation on how to combat and how to deal with rodents.

526
00:49:06,654 --> 00:49:09,457
[SPEAKER_08]: And their main point is that killing them with

527
00:49:10,125 --> 00:49:12,246
[SPEAKER_08]: with rodenticides is not the answer.

528
00:49:12,446 --> 00:49:20,508
[SPEAKER_08]: It has to be integrated pest control plan that residents would have.

529
00:49:21,089 --> 00:49:27,691
[SPEAKER_08]: And they really didn't recommend poisons and killing because it doesn't really work because of the way they multiply.

530
00:49:28,371 --> 00:49:38,034
